high_descs: walk to the kitchen counter to the right of the fridge just up ahead on the left
grab a knife off of the kitchen counter there
cut up the tomato on the kitchen counter to your right
look up and move over to the front of the fridge to your left
place the knife down inside of the fridge there
turn right and walk to the kitchen counter, then turn left to face it
grab a tomato slice off of the kitchen counter there
move left to the front of the fridge again
place the tomato slice inside of the fridge, let it cool, then take it back out
turn right and walk over to the microwave on the right side of the room
place the tomato slice inside of the microwave
anns.task_desc: place a cooled tomato slice inside of the microwave

high_descs: Walk to the counter
Pick the knife up from the counter
Take the knife to the counter that is in the middle of the room
Grab the knife from the counter and place it in the fridge
Walk to the counter and pick up a piece of bread
Take the bread to the fridge
Put the bread in the fridge
Take the bread out of the fridge
Carry the bread to the microwave
Place the bread in the microwave
Close the microwave door and turn it on
Walk to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the knife on the edge of the counter.
Slice the tomato on the counter.
Walk to the left to the refrigerator.
Put the knife on the bottom shelf above the drawers.
Walk back to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Walk back to the refrigerator.
Put the tomato next to the knife in the refrigerator for a few seconds, pick up the tomato slice again.
Turn around, walk around the counter, go to the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: Move forward past the refrigerator and turn to your left at the counter top between the refrigerator and the stove.
Pick up the knife on the edge of the counter, in front of the red pepper.
Cut off the stem and slice the red pepper, on the counter, next to the stove.
Turn to your left and face the front of the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator door placing the knife on the shelf below the coffee mug, then shut the refrigerator door.
Turn back to the counter top that is between the refrigerator and the stove,  to your right.
Pick up a piece of the sliced pepper.
Go back in front of the refrigerator to your left.
Place the sliced pepper in the refrigerator, on the shelf next to the knife, wait a moment,  then remove the pepper.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, past the island, and turn to your left at the microwave.
Place the sliced pepper in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a pepper slice in the microwave.

high_descs: Walk forward then turn right and face the counter that has a knife and tomato on it.
Pick up the yellow knife on the counter.
Slice the tomato on the counter but do not put down the knife.
Turn to the left and walk over to the fridge.
Place the knife inside the fridge and shut the door.
Turn right and walk forward to the counter.
Pick up a tomato slice on the counter.
Turn left and walk forward a little then turn right to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the tomato slice inside. Then open and take the slice out.
Turn to the right and walk forward. Then turn to the left and face the microwave.
Place the tomato slice inside the microwave and shut the door.
